title: Infant mortality rate in the Netherlands 2008 to 2018
yAxis: Infant mortality per 1,000 live born children
summary: Overall Infant mortality per 1,000 live born children has decreased over the Year.
Infant mortality per 1,000 live born children is slightly decreasing from 2013 to 2014.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Infant mortality per 1,000 live born children, of value 3.8 was reached at Year 2013
The lowest Infant mortality per 1,000 live born children, of value 3.6 was reported at Year 2014
